snippet.title: Way to Go! Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Have fun watching the trailer of our new game "Way to Go!".
Download the FREE DEMO from our website:
http://www.waytogo-game.com/index.php?cat=Demo&page=Demo

The demo is available for PC, Mac and Linux.
